  <summary date="2020-01-13T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Critical Habitat Improvement Act

This bill revises requirements governing the designation of critical habitat for an endangered or threatened species.&#160;Habitats outside of the geographical area occupied by&#160;the species must have at least one physical or biological feature that is essential to the conservation of the species in order to be considered as a potential critical habitat.</summary>
